==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One arrow, two eagles.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī jiàn shuāng diāo

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[箭]][[双]][[雕]]'''

# [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals.

===Alternate forms===
[[一箭雙雕]], [[一箭雙鵰]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
[[一石二鸟]]
[[一举两得]]
[[一挙両得]] ([[Japanese]])

